<SYNC Start=736602><P Class=ENCC>
She may not even know.
<SYNC Start=738160><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=738471><P Class=ENCC>
I haven't heard from her in seven<br>months, what else is it about?
<SYNC Start=744000><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=744210><P Class=ENCC>
She was my best friend.
<SYNC Start=746235><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=746512><P Class=ENCC>
