<SYNC Start=849981><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=860092><P Class=ENCC>
I'm gonna ask once,<br>and I want a straight answer.
<SYNC Start=863357><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=863562><P Class=ENCC>
