-Okay, I'm just gonna say it.<br>-Okay.
<SYNC Start=883181><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=885284><P Class=ENCC>
Will you be my maid of honor?
<SYNC Start=888014><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
