If it'll make you feel any better...
<SYNC Start=932897><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=933165><P Class=ENCC>
...when Barry and I got engaged,<br>he was weird too.
<SYNC Start=936566><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
