... kind of had<br>a little thing on the side.
<SYNC Start=952181><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=953052><P Class=ENCC>
-What?<br>-I know, I know.
<SYNC Start=955247><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=955454><P Class=ENCC>
When he proposed, people said, "He'll<br>do to you what he did to Rachel."
<SYNC Start=960517><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=960726><P Class=ENCC>
And now I feel so stupid.
<SYNC Start=963058><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=967433><P Class=ENCC>
You are so stupid.
<SYNC Start=968832><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=971437><P Class=ENCC>
