<SYNC Start=1070327><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1071003><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, so what?
<SYNC Start=1072800><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1073138><P Class=ENCC>
I live across the street, and I know<br>about your telescope.
