<SYNC Start=1077609><P Class=ENCC>
And I don't appreciate it.
<SYNC Start=1079338><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1079611><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, I can see you right now.<br>Hello?
