If I wanna walk around in my<br>underwear, I shouldn't have to feel
<SYNC Start=1087684><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1087886><P Class=ENCC>
Thank you.
<SYNC Start=1089547><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1091557><P Class=ENCC>
That's not really the point.<br>The point is, that
<SYNC Start=1095220><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1095427><P Class=ENCC>
Mostly free-weights,<br>but occasionally
<SYNC Start=1098521><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1100466><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah, my neighbor.<br>Yeah, the brunette.
<SYNC Start=1103026><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1104570><P Class=ENCC>
She said you looked pretty that day<br>in the green dress.
