<SYNC Start=1127523><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1128026><P Class=ENCC>
It's a leave-in conditioner, okay?
<SYNC Start=1131257><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1132097><P Class=ENCC>
It's a leave-in conditioner.
<SYNC Start=1134691><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1139271><P Class=ENCC>
-You got a second?<br>-Sure, sure.
