<SYNC Start=1141340><P Class=ENCC>
Come on...
<SYNC Start=1142432><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1143041><P Class=ENCC>
-...in.<br>-Hello, sweetheart.
<SYNC Start=1145703><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1146578><P Class=ENCC>
What you guys doing here?
<SYNC Start=1148341><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1148580><P Class=ENCC>
