<SYNC Start=1159453><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1160893><P Class=ENCC>
I'm sorry.<br>God, I am so sorry.
<SYNC Start=1163020><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1163262><P Class=ENCC>
I was weak.<br>I couldn't help myself.
<SYNC Start=1165628><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1165898><P Class=ENCC>
Whatever I did, I only did<br>because I love you so much.
<SYNC Start=1170062><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1171403><P Class=ENCC>
Which one of us<br>are you talking to there?
<SYNC Start=1174804><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1176742><P Class=ENCC>
Mindy.
<SYNC Start=1177902><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1178143><P Class=ENCC>
Of course, Mindy.<br>It was always Mindy.
<SYNC Start=1180634><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1181013><P Class=ENCC>
When we were having sex<br>in that chair?
<SYNC Start=1183379><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1183815><P Class=ENCC>
