<SYNC Start=1199259><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1199998><P Class=ENCC>
Honey, sweetheart, look.<br>Just give me another chance.
<SYNC Start=1203729><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
