<SYNC Start=1206769><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1206972><P Class=ENCC>
What is it with you and Aruba?<br>Do you have a deal with the airlines?
<SYNC Start=1211966><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1212778><P Class=ENCC>
What do you say?
<SYNC Start=1214075><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1214346><P Class=ENCC>
Dr. Farber, we've got<br>an emergency here.
<SYNC Start=1217008><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1217282><P Class=ENCC>
