<SYNC Start=1219910><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1220185><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, God.<br>I'll be right there, Bernice.
<SYNC Start=1222983><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
