<SYNC Start=1278472><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1278744><P Class=ENCC>
And I hope you'll still be<br>my maid of honor.
<SYNC Start=1282180><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1282447><P Class=ENCC>
