<SYNC Start=1357718><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1357956><P Class=ENCC>
So I thought I'd come down here<br>and make sure you were okay.
<SYNC Start=1362393><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1362594><P Class=ENCC>
